Upgrade a Cloud Essentials for OpenSearch deployment.

USAGE:
  scw searchdb deployment upgrade [arg=value ...]

ARGS:
  deployment-id         UUID of the Deployment to upgrade
  [node-count]          The target number of nodes for the upgrade.
  [volume-size-bytes]   Volume size upgrade target
  [region=fr-par]       Region to target. If none is passed will use default region from the config (fr-par)

DEPRECATED ARGS:
  [node-amount]   DEPRECATED: Use node_count instead. Amount of node upgrade target

FLAGS:
  -h, --help                help for upgrade
      --list-sub-commands   List all subcommands

GLOBAL FLAGS:
  -c, --config string    The path to the config file
  -D, --debug            Enable debug mode
  -o, --output string    Output format: json or human, see 'scw help output' for more info (default "human")
  -p, --profile string   The config profile to use
